---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog
description: Insights on productivity, screenshots, and health tracking from the Visionion team.
---

<header class="blog-header">
  <h1 class="blog-title">Visionion Blog</h1>
  <p class="blog-subtitle">Insights on productivity, screenshots, and health tracking.</p>
</header>

<nav class="category-nav">
  <a href="/blog/" class="category-link active">All</a>
  <a href="/blog/category/focusguard/" class="category-link">FocusGuard</a>
  <a href="/blog/category/snapp/" class="category-link">Snapp</a>
  <a href="/blog/category/endurotrack/" class="category-link">EnduroTrack</a>
</nav>

<div class="posts-list">
  {%- for post in collections.posts -%}
  <a href="/blog{{ post.url }}" class="post-card">
    <div class="post-meta">
      <span class="post-category {{ post.data.category }}">{{ post.data.category }}</span>
      <time class="post-date" datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
    </div>
    <h2 class="post-card-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
    <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
  </a>
  {%- endfor -%}
</div>

